SPELL NAME  : Flamestrike
SPELL SYNTAX: Flamestrike 
SPELL COST  : 150 SP
DESCRIPTION : This spell causes flames to shower down from the heavens
              and cause massive damage to all the creatures in the
              room except the caster, his pets and allies.

Note        : Non-PK players will never get hit with this skill and
              PK players only get hit if the caster is PK too. Due
              to a recent update of the skill you will now be able
              to always cast this spell, even if there are players
              in the room that will not be affected.

